2.The HRMO record leave applications, computes and deducts under time and coordinate with the different departments on matters pertaining to employees’ leave applications; 

3.The Municipal Accountant ensures that every claim for salaries and wages is supported with complete documents particularly the approved DTRs; and

4.The LGU to repair the Biometric to faithfully record the attendance of personnel.

It is recommended that the management;

comply with the provisions of in COA Circular No. 2013-004 by providing this Office the list of all on-going government PPAs as of December 31, 2016 and specific information as mentioned above with regards to infrastructure projects;
inform this Office within 10 days after the award of the infrastructure project or before the start of the program/activity that the appropriate project signboards and/or public notices are already posted; and
prepare and submit to this Office the monthly monitoring report.

